snippet.title: The Channel F Files Videocart #8 Magic Numbers and NIM!
snippet.description:
Some "logic" games for the ole Channel F :)  I actually really enjoy these :)   In Magic Numbers you try to guess what number the Channel F is thinking of, in NIM you have to try to make the Channel F the last one to remove a number from the piles.  Very challenging game.
The Channel F Files Podcast Blog - http://thechannelffiles.blogspot.com/
The Channel F Files Facebook Page - https://www.facebook.com/TheChannelFFiles
